These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, cat, guinea-pig, fish
4 different games are played: canasta, billiard, monopoly, backgammon
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, video-games, photography, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, satire, adventure, sports
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, skateboard, subway
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
 3. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
 4. the person playing canasta is the person watching satire movies##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
 7. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 9. the person driving the subway is the owner of the horse##1
10. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
11. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
12. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
13. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
14. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
15. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
16. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Pet    | fish | cat     | guinea-pig     | horse |
| Game        | billiard  | canasta | monopoly      | backgammon      |
| Hobby         | hiking  | video-games    | photography | filmmaking       |
| Movie-Genre       | scientific | satire   | adventure      | sports  |
| Transport   | bus      | airplane  | skateboard   | subway      |

