10. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
11. the modern house is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
12. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
13. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
