 9. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
10. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
11. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
12. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
